Package: GeneClassesPackage
Title: A Package About Genes to Help Biologists
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Elena", "Sasso", email = "elena.sasso@mail.polimi.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides classes and functions to help biologists
    work with genetic data. The package includes a generic virtual gene class and
    other specific gene classes divided into 3 main categories: protein-coding,
    housekeeping RNA (including tRNA genes and rRNA genes), and non-coding RNA.
